  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Playground Equipment Installation supervisor",
  "description": "<p>Playland Sports Pte Ltd, a specialist for playground and fitness equipment installation and managing and maintenance, her mission is to create happier, healthier playground and fitness corner.</p><p>We are looking for an experienced Site Supervisor<strong> </strong>who is interesting with the playground and fitness equipment, solving the installation issues, and ensuring every equipment's installed runs smoothly and make the safety and timely of delivery with high quality. Join us as a Site Supervisor and together we move forward.<br /></p><p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTIONS</strong></p><p>1) Work together with playground design engineer.</p><p>2) Study the installation manuals, design drawing and specifications, and give correct instructions and guidance to the installation workers.</p><p>3) Supervise site installation and make sure the installation to be delivered safely, correctly, and fast with high standard quality.</p><p>4) Discuss with client for the problems arise and make necessary repair and troubleshooting.</p><p>5) Negotiate with manufacturer partners to make sure the equipment can be installed correctly and smoothly on site.</p><p>6) Arrange repair, maintenance and servicing of all equipment and make sure all equipment are in good condition of working.</p><p><em> 7</em>) Part time working can be considered.<br /></p><p><em></em></p>",
